ARTWORK AND INSPIRATION NOTICE

This MIT license applies to the source code and repository materials distributed
as part of this project.

The tamer artwork used in Verdal: A Tamer's Journey was created by jameslu06 for an
earlier character-customizer project and adapted for use in this game.

Some of the creature artwork used in this project was also drawn by jameslu06, but
those creature designs originated as fan-made Pokémon-inspired / Pokémon-derived
artwork from the earlier customizer project rather than as fully original
creature concepts.

Verdal: A Tamer's Journey is an unofficial fan-made project inspired by classic
monster-taming RPGs. Pokémon and related franchise elements are the property of
Nintendo, Game Freak, and Creatures Inc. This project is not affiliated with or
endorsed by those companies.

If this project is redistributed publicly beyond personal or educational use,
or developed commercially, the Pokémon-derived creature artwork should be
replaced or redesigned into fully original creature designs.

See README.md and CREDITS.md for additional attribution and project notes.
